FlipView Like FlipBoard
================================================

Flipboard came with their awesome Magazine Style Layout and rendering of Views which leads to get inspire us and after a long thought & discussions we came up with simple idea of arranging Layout/View in a way which is quite a look like functionality of FlipBoard.

We implemented feature like:

- Random layout selection*
- Arranging view while changing orientation
- Page Flip 
- FullScreen View when Click

